<section
  class="overflow-hidden bg-cover bg-top bg-no-repeat"
  style="background-image: url(<%= image_url "college.jpg" %>)"
  id="about"
>
  <div class="bg-black/70 p-8 md:p-12 lg:px-40 lg:py-24">
    <div class="text-center sm:text-right">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white sm:text-3xl md:text-5xl">
        What's this about?
      </h2>

      <div class="flex">
        <div class="md:w-1/3 lg:w-1/2"></div>
        <div class="md:w-2/3 lg:w-1/2">
            <p class="text-white mt-3 md:mt-4">
              Faculty are called to our jobs out of the love
              of research and teaching. So why must so much of our time be spent on tedious
              logistics outside of our core mission?
            </p>

            <p class="text-white mt-3 md:mt-4">
              We created <span class="font-bold">ScholarLattice</span> to help. With just
              a few clicks, you can organize your next seminar or conference, complete with
              online registration, abstract management, and payment processing.
            </p>
            <div class="mt-4 md:mt-8">
              <a
                href="/collections"
                class="inline-block rounded bg-sky-600 px-12 py-3 text-sm font-medium text-white transition hover:bg-sky-700 focus:outline-none focus:ring focus:ring-blue-400"
              >
                Connect with your community
              </a>
            </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
